flowchart LR
  classDef actor fill:#ffe066,stroke:#d4a100,color:#3d2f00;
  classDef command fill:#6db3f2,stroke:#1c6fb8,color:#08243d;
  classDef aggregate fill:#fff2ae,stroke:#c9a900,color:#4a3b00;
  classDef event fill:#ffb84d,stroke:#d47500,color:#4a2600;
  classDef integration fill:#ff8c42,stroke:#c0501a,color:#3d1500;
  classDef readmodel fill:#b5e7a0,stroke:#4f9a2f,color:#1f3d0f;
  classDef external fill:#ffb6c1,stroke:#d63b6a,color:#4a0a1c;

  VISITOR([🎬 Visitor]):::actor
  USER([🎬 User]):::actor
  ADMIN([🎬 Administrator]):::actor

  C_SIGNUP[⚡ SignUp]:::command
  C_SIGNIN[⚡ SignIn]:::command
  C_RECOVER[⚡ RecoverPassword]:::command
  C_RESET[⚡ ResetPassword]:::command
  C_PROFILE[⚡ UpdateProfile]:::command
  C_UIPREF[⚡ UpdateUiPreference]:::command
  C_ASSIGN[⚡ AssignAccessProfile]:::command
  C_DELETE[⚡ DeleteAccount]:::command

  A_USER[📦 User]:::aggregate
  A_ACCESS[📦 AccessProfile]:::aggregate
  A_UIPREF[📦 UserUiPreference]:::aggregate

  E_USER_REG[🟠 UserRegistered]:::event
  IE_USER_REG[🔗 UserRegisteredIntegrationEvent]:::integration
  JWT[🟢 JWT Session]:::readmodel

  VISITOR --> C_SIGNUP --> A_USER --> E_USER_REG --> IE_USER_REG
  USER --> C_SIGNIN --> A_USER --> JWT
  VISITOR --> C_RECOVER --> A_USER
  USER --> C_RESET --> A_USER
  USER --> C_PROFILE --> A_USER
  USER --> C_UIPREF --> A_UIPREF
  ADMIN --> C_ASSIGN --> A_ACCESS
  A_ACCESS -.roles/permissions.-> A_USER
  USER --> C_DELETE --> A_USER

  IE_USER_REG -->|consumed by Notifications and Reporting| OUT([🔗 to Notifications + Reporting]):::integration
